    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly and shows signs of a possible head gasket leak, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several deep scratches and dents across the body. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, and I strongly recommend a professional inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
